{"lastModified":1764236742215,"uri":"c::8275378522::vessel::bae583a0-78c8-11ee-9cb1-37f6e3e1ee0a","yachtType":["Motor"],"description":"Summer/Winter Operating Area: Caribbean - U.S. Virgin Islands, British Virgin Islands, Leeward Islands, Windward Islands\n\nNauti Nickel left no luxury to spare with the finest attention to detail in mind, curating an idyllic Caribbean charter experience. Newly splashed in 2023, Nauti Nickel is built to accommodate four crew to serve up to 10 guests. Sleek, elegant, and extremely spacious with an overall length of 80 feet and beam of 40 feet; Nauti Nickel truly is the hallmark of cruising comfort.\n\nHer flybridge hosts two open seating areas, a TV, bar, grill, and jacuzzi. Equipped with an ice maker and refrigerator stocked with your favorites drinks, chilled water, and seltzer on tap, bar service follows you to this space. The overhead bimini provides an area of escape from the sun for those who want shade or integrated lighting for evening cocktails. The expansive aft lounge cushion for sun bathing makes this a highly desirable space for relaxation, reading, or napping,\nall enjoyed with panoramic views of the surrounding scenery.\n\nThe protected aft deck provides additional lounging spaces in addition to an elegant setting for formal dining. Two lounge pads are optimal for relaxing as well as another area aft of the dining table.\n\nEntering the salon area, urban chic decor with leather upholstery with a customized backlit bar welcomes guests to a fully air conditioned interior. This space highlights an additional dining area and comfort zone for a morning coffee or evening chess match. The open galley is equipped with state of the art appliances, fine china,\nand extensive glassware. The Electrolux Gourmet Coffee maker grinds fresh coffee with\neach cup and froths your milk with the precision of a swiss watch. Two inbuilt wine chillers ensure the meals will consistently be paired with the selected wines.\n\nNauti Nickel is equipped with a large array of water toys including, a jet ski, sea bobs, snorkel gear, kayaks, stand-\nup paddleboards, adult and children wakeboards, water skis, noodles, floating lily pad, and a range of towable inflatables.\n\nNauti Nickel's crew of four are waiting for the opportunity create an experience you will never forget.","blueprint":{"name":"NAUTI NICKEL","images":["/media/media::image::c::8275378522::vessel::bae583a0-78c8-11ee-9cb1-37f6e3e1ee0a::assets::b84d4b50-7972-11ee-9d31-c506321dd6f5.png/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8275378522::vessel::bae583a0-78c8-11ee-9cb1-37f6e3e1ee0a::assets::1ec894a0-78cb-11ee-9cb1-37f6e3e1ee0a.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8275378522::vessel::bae583a0-78c8-11ee-9cb1-37f6e3e1ee0a::assets::42490540-78cb-11ee-9cb1-37f6e3e1ee0a.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8275378522::vessel::bae583a0-78c8-11ee-9cb1-37f6e3e1ee0a::assets::42481ae0-78cb-11ee-9cb1-37f6e3e1ee0a.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8275378522::vessel::bae583a0-78c8-11ee-9cb1-37f6e3e1ee0a::assets::53980530-78cb-11ee-9cb1-37f6e3e1ee0a.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8275378522::vessel::bae583a0-78c8-11ee-9cb1-37f6e3e1ee0a::assets::539741e0-78cb-11ee-9cb1-37f6e3e1ee0a.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8275378522::vessel::bae583a0-78c8-11ee-9cb1-37f6e3e1ee0a::assets::6024e930-78cb-11ee-9cb1-37f6e3e1ee0a.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8275378522::vessel::bae583a0-78c8-11ee-9cb1-37f6e3e1ee0a::assets::6024c220-78cb-11ee-9cb1-37f6e3e1ee0a.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8275378522::vessel::bae583a0-78c8-11ee-9cb1-37f6e3e1ee0a::assets::6021b4e0-78cb-11ee-9cb1-37f6e3e1ee0a.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8275378522::vessel::bae583a0-78c8-11ee-9cb1-37f6e3e1ee0a::assets::2ced2fa0-78cb-11ee-9cb1-37f6e3e1ee0a.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8275378522::vessel::bae583a0-78c8-11ee-9cb1-37f6e3e1ee0a::assets::60229f40-78cb-11ee-9cb1-37f6e3e1ee0a.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8275378522::vessel::bae583a0-78c8-11ee-9cb1-37f6e3e1ee0a::assets::1ec7d150-78cb-11ee-9cb1-37f6e3e1ee0a.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8275378522::vessel::bae583a0-78c8-11ee-9cb1-37f6e3e1ee0a::assets::6023fed0-78cb-11ee-9cb1-37f6e3e1ee0a.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8275378522::vessel::bae583a0-78c8-11ee-9cb1-37f6e3e1ee0a::assets::602389a0-78cb-11ee-9cb1-37f6e3e1ee0a.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8275378522::vessel::bae583a0-78c8-11ee-9cb1-37f6e3e1ee0a::assets::6023d7c0-78cb-11ee-9cb1-37f6e3e1ee0a.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8275378522::vessel::bae583a0-78c8-11ee-9cb1-37f6e3e1ee0a::assets::60244cf0-78cb-11ee-9cb1-37f6e3e1ee0a.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8275378522::vessel::bae583a0-78c8-11ee-9cb1-37f6e3e1ee0a::assets::556cb1c0-9eb5-11ee-ae63-238241601caf.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8275378522::vessel::bae583a0-78c8-11ee-9cb1-37f6e3e1ee0a::assets::60233b80-78cb-11ee-9cb1-37f6e3e1ee0a.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8275378522::vessel::bae583a0-78c8-11ee-9cb1-37f6e3e1ee0a::assets::6022ed60-78cb-11ee-9cb1-37f6e3e1ee0a.jpeg/{imageVariant}"],"make":"Sunreef Yachts","model":"","maxCrew":4,"sleeps":10,"basePort":{"uri":"a::place::a0201b56-b3ee-11ed-8a74-325096b39f47","name":"Tortola","coordinates":{"latitude":18.4335216,"longitude":-64.63325746},"country":"British Virgin Islands"},"builtYear":2023,"refitYear":"","topSpeed":22,"cruiseSpeed":12,"fuelCapacity":"","cabinLayout":[{"label":"Master Cabin","value":"1"},{"label":"Queen Cabin","value":"3"},{"label":"Twin Cabin","value":"1"}],"cabins":5,"bathrooms":6,"decks":"","length":24.38,"beam":12.19,"draft":2.29,"hullType":"","hullConstruction":"","tonnage":"","superStructure":[],"engines":"2 x Man 1200hp ","amenities":[{"label":"Air Conditioning"},{"label":"Jacuzzi"},{"label":"Sun Awning"},{"label":"Children Allowed"},{"label":"Generators","quantity":"2"},{"label":"Ice Maker","quantity":"2"},{"label":"Hairdryers"},{"label":"Inverter"},{"label":"BBQ"},{"label":"Deck Shower"},{"label":"Water Maker"},{"label":"Bimini"},{"label":"Wine cooler","quantity":"2"},{"label":"Extra fridges and freezers"},{"label":"Medical kit to MCA coding"},{"label":"Re-usable water bottles"},{"label":"Purified drinking water"},{"label":"Flybridge"},{"label":"Shaded Bow area"},{"label":"Dinghy lift on the aft transom"},{"label":"USB and wireless cell phone chargers"},{"label":"Bar"},{"label":"Sunbathing Area"},{"label":"Lounge Pads","quantity":"2"},{"label":"Coffee Maker"}],"toys":[{"label":"Jet Skis"},{"label":"Tube"},{"label":"SU Paddle Boards","quantity":"2"},{"label":"Underwater Camera"},{"label":"Swim Platform"},{"label":"Fishing Gear","quantity":"2"},{"label":"Underwater Video"},{"label":"Adult wakeboard"},{"label":"Boarding Ladder"},{"label":"Water Skis Adult"},{"label":"Snorkel Gear","quantity":"10"},{"label":"Kayaks (2 Pax)"},{"label":"Beach Games"},{"label":"Deep Sea Fish"},{"label":"Sea Bobs with Cameras","quantity":"2"},{"label":"Towable Inflatables"},{"label":"“Lily Pad” floating lounger"},{"label":"Junior wakeboard"}],"entertainment":["Wi-Fi","Salon TV","Salon Stereo","Satellite TV","iPod/Device Hookups","Denon Music","SMART Samsung TVs"],"tenders":["Williams 520 Sport Jet Tender with\t200hp engine (10 pax)"]},"crew":[{"name":"Michael Lang","avatar":"/media/media::image::c::8275378522::vessel::bae583a0-78c8-11ee-9cb1-37f6e3e1ee0a::assets::3ac4f1f0-3baa-11f0-9d04-49aaac885be6/{imageVariant}","role":"Captain","bio":"The heart of Nauti Nickel is the husband-and-wife team of Michael and Jennifer Lang, seasoned professionals with over 70 luxury term charters under their belts. Their connection is effortless, their energy magnetic, and their passion for creating unforgettable experiences contagious.\n\nMichael, originally from California, serves as both Captain and onboard Engineer. His calm command of the vessel and deep systems knowledge bring safety and confidence to every journey. But more than that, his joy in working side-by-side with Jennifer creates a seamless experience for guests—one where every detail feels thoughtful and perfectly orchestrated.\n\nTogether, Michael and Jennifer lead with intention, joy, and an infectious sense of adventure—welcoming each guest not just onto a yacht, but into their world"},{"name":"Jennifer Lang","avatar":"/media/media::image::c::8275378522::vessel::bae583a0-78c8-11ee-9cb1-37f6e3e1ee0a::assets::467ef590-3baa-11f0-9d04-49aaac885be6/{imageVariant}","role":"Captain","bio":"Jennifer, a Le Cordon Bleu–trained chef with French roots and global influences, delights guests with meals that are vibrant, elevated, and full of soul. Her career began in Portland’s fine dining scene, and her menus now reflect a love for local Caribbean flavors with upscale finesse. A natural hostess, Jennifer blends refined service with heartfelt warmth—making every guest feel like family."},{"name":"Kelanie Torres","avatar":"/media/media::image::c::8275378522::vessel::bae583a0-78c8-11ee-9cb1-37f6e3e1ee0a::assets::5a7ff620-3baa-11f0-9d04-49aaac885be6/{imageVariant}","role":"Captain","bio":"Born and raised in Puerto Rico, Kelanie is the soul of Caribbean adventure. With eight years in the boating industry and a background in marine mechanics, she brings a deep knowledge of the sea—and the vessel—to every charter. Guests love her energy and expertise, whether she’s leading snorkeling excursions, handling the tender for a beach picnic, or sharing her favorite hidden coves. From surfing to spearfishing, Kelanie’s island spirit infuses the entire experience with authenticity and excitement."},{"name":"Seth Swart","avatar":"/media/media::image::c::8275378522::vessel::bae583a0-78c8-11ee-9cb1-37f6e3e1ee0a::assets::6601d2c0-3baa-11f0-9d04-49aaac885be6/{imageVariant}","role":"Captain","bio":"Reliable, energetic, and always up for an adventure, Seth brings three years of professional yachting experience and a lifetime of ocean passion to his role as deckhand. Also from Mossel Bay, he’s a certified personal trainer with a love for fitness and action. Whether launching water toys, maintaining the yacht’s sleek profile, or guiding paddleboard sessions, Seth’s steady presence and hands-on skills help keep the experience smooth, safe, and full of fun."},{"name":"Camilla Vosloo","avatar":"/media/media::image::c::8275378522::vessel::bae583a0-78c8-11ee-9cb1-37f6e3e1ee0a::assets::71064200-3baa-11f0-9d04-49aaac885be6/{imageVariant}","role":"Captain","bio":"With her radiant smile and calming presence, Camilla transforms the onboard atmosphere into one of effortless elegance and tranquility. Born and raised in the seaside town of Mossel Bay, South Africa, she’s a certified Master Scuba Diver who finds joy in sharing the wonders of the ocean. Her hospitality background and intuitive service style create a boutique-hotel feel aboard Nauti Nickel, where every detail—from towel folds to tablescapes—is infused with care and creativity."}],"pricing":{"weekPricingFrom":{"currency":"USD","price":10400000,"displayCurrency":"USD","displayPrice":10400000,"unit":"WEEK"},"weekPricingTo":{"currency":"USD","price":12000000,"displayCurrency":"USD","displayPrice":12000000,"unit":"WEEK"},"pricingInfo":[{"name":"Summer/Winter - Low Season","effectiveDates":[{"from":"2025-05-01T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2025-12-14T23:59:59.999Z"},{"from":"2026-05-01T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2026-12-14T23:59:59.999Z"},{"from":"2027-05-01T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2027-12-14T23:59:59.999Z"}],"pricing":{"note":"","currency":"USD","inputAmountTaxed":"INCLUSIVE","subTotal":10400000,"totalTax":0,"total":10400000,"lineItems":[{"item":"Charter Fee","conditions":"VAT is Included","quantity":1,"unitPrice":10400000,"amount":10400000}],"charterFee":10400000,"unit":"WEEK"},"inclusionZones":[{"label":"Anguilla","type":"Dependency","category":["North America","Caribbean","Anguilla"],"coordinates":[-63.06498926535688,18.22395950228264],"bbox":[-63.160